1. Primary Emotions of Statements (https://data.world/crowdflower/primary-emotions-of-statements) a small dataset, labelled with Robert Plutchik emotion wheel
2. NRC emotion lexicon (http://sentiment.nrc.ca/lexicons-for-research/) a dataset for lexicon labelled with 8 emotions and 2 polarities
3. http://saifmohammad.com/WebPages/SentimentEmotionLabeledData.html 一个很多的数据集
4. SemEval-2018 Task 1: Affect in Tweets (AIT-2018) e-c dataset (https://competitions.codalab.org/competitions/17751#learn_the_details-datasets) 推特数据集,有八种情绪，但是每一个推特可能有多种情绪
5 .Dataset for Emotions of Narrative Sequences(https://arxiv.org/pdf/1910.11769.pdf) 八种情感的数据集，来源比较奇怪， 同时去除了 trust 加入了love
